{"tid":2425041,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[第五波疫情正式啟動！！] 疫情持續反彈　消息指新增 33 宗確診","createTime":"2021-02-27T05:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T05:34:50.000Z","uid":184822,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"63fc85de42640d34180cbd42ff801acba1a90fbe","tid":2425041,"uid":184822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T05:34:50.000Z","msg":"本港武漢肺炎疫情持續反彈，消息人士向《立場新聞》表示，今日（27 日）新增 33 宗確診個案。政府專家顧問之一，中大呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌向《立場新聞》表示，相信是因為農曆年假「新年後遺症」，及 K11 Musea 名潮食館有群組爆發，令確診數回升。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%88-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E-33-%E5%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A2%259E-33-%25E5%25AE%2597%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%2F&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm8sFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=6d1a6b9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A2%259E-33-%25E5%25AE%2597%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%2F&h=4b55beb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%88-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E-33-%E5%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nK11群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}